- [ ] After successful login, enumerate all newly visible links, forms, and API endpoints.
- [ ] For every ID-like value discovered (e.g., `user_id`, account numbers, order IDs, path segments like `/password/<username>`), fuzz with nearby and pattern-based values to test for IDOR or authorization issues.
