ased HTML, jQuery 3.5.1, bootstrap.bundle.js (from script/link tags)\n\n- **Authentication / Session Management**:\n  - Login endpoint:\n    - POST /password/test\n    - Request body (URL-encoded form):\n      - username=test&user_id=10032&password=test\n    - Successful login returns HTTP 302 FOUND with Location header and sets a session cookie.\n  - Session cookie:\n    - Name: session\n    - Value: eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoxMDAzMn0.aVJgzA.uZZMmFq9xMGkcoVmdlwJJtMVX9I\n    - Attributes: HttpOnly; Path=/\n    - Appears to encode user_id 10032 in its payload (from value structure), but this is not exploited yet.\n  - Post-login redirect:\n    - Location: /dashboard?username=test\n    - Following redirect with the session cookie results in HTTP 200 OK and dashboard HTML.\n  - Authenticated-only pages (require session cookie):\n    - /orders (tested: 200 OK only when Cookie: session=eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoxMDAzMn0.aVJgzA.uZZMmFq9xMGkcoVmdlwJJtMVX9I present)\n    - /orders_archive (same cookie requirement)\n  - Logout mechanism:\n    - POST /logout via a form in the navbar (seen on dashboard, orders, orders_archive). No direct request was issued in this phase, so behavior is not yet confirmed.\n\n- **Full Working HTTP Requests & Responses (Evidence)**:\n\n1) **Login and Redirect to Dashboard**\n\n**Request**:\n```\nPOST /password/test HTTP/1.1\nHost: 127.0.0.1:32930\nUser-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36\nAccept: */*\nContent-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\nContent-Length: 46\n\nusername=test&user_id=10032&password=test\n```\n\n**Response**:\n```\nHTTP/1.1 302 FOUND\ndate: Mon, 29 Dec 2025 11:06:52 GMT\nserver: Apache/2.4.65 (Debian)\ncontent-length: 235\nlocation: /dashboard?username=test\ncache-control: public, max-age=0\npragma: no-cache\nexpires: 0\nvary: Cookie\nset-cookie: session=eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoxMDAzMn0.aVJgzA.uZZMmFq9xMGkcoVmdlwJJtMVX9I; HttpOnly; Path=/\nkeep-alive: timeout=5, max=100\nconnection: Keep-Alive\ncontent-type: text/html; c